<item>
            <title>[LU-7698] &apos;lctl debug_list&apos; information is incorrect</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7698</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;These two commands print possible parameter values of &quot;all_subs&quot; and &quot;all_types&quot;, respectively.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl debug_list subs&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl debug_list types&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Their output is inaccurate.  The values &quot;all_subs&quot; and &quot;all_types&quot; are implemented, in both cases, as the value &quot;all&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
